Subject: CHANGE: choice in verilog-ams model
Date: Thu, 20 May 2010 11:55:11 -0600
X-Mailer: Apple Mail (2.936)

When there is a choice place with expressions and no delay, it should  
be translated as follows:

p0 - {e and e1}[0,0] -> t1
p0 - {e and e2}[0,0] -> t2

Assume e1 and e2 is false.

always@(cross(e))
	if (e1)
		fire t1
	elsif (e2)
		fire t2

always@(place)
	if (p0)
		if (e and e1)
			fire t1
		elsif (e and e2)
			fire t2

